  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2009-04-02",
    "date": "2009-04-29T14:45:41Z",
    "text": "Border Fence Trust Fund Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to establish in the Treasury the Border Improvement Trust Fund and allow individual taxpayers (other than nonresident aliens) to designate that $5.00 ($10.00 in the case of joint returns) of their income taxes be paid over to such Fund to install additional barriers and roads at the U.S. border."
